        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">UH — 5 Points</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">H is worth 4 points. One more point than UM. Fewer extensions but higher base score. Better for pure scoring, worse for setup plays.</p></div>
      </div>

